  "_risk_metrics_readme": "RISK/POSITION split (Option 1, 2026-06-24) — DAVID-CURATED, never a heuristic. A risk-framed signal is an ABSENCE/exposure no pay strategy excuses (statutory-adjacent / duty-of-care floor), distinct from a position-framed DISTANCE a deliberate strategy explains. Listed qids get signal.risk_framed=true; the client gives them a coral accent, and per-domain suppression (step 3) will EXEMPT them so a deliberate-lag domain can never hide a genuine floor (the maternity-zero guard). Add a qid only when its absence is a floor, not a position.",
  "risk_metrics": ["REW_BEN_FAM_002", "REW262_TIME_SICKDAYONE", "REW26_WEL_EAP"],
  "_variable_pay_metrics_readme": "VARIABLE_PAY tag (step-3 tagging pass, 2026-06-25) — DAVID-CURATED, never a heuristic. Upgrades the pay_for_performance re-rank from COARSE domain==Incentives keying to PRECISE per-metric: only these qids get the P4P multiplier (strong 1.4 / egal 0.7). Variable pay = pay contingent on performance/outcome — a bonus/LTI/commission AMOUNT or OPPORTUNITY, or the EXISTENCE of such a vehicle. NOT: incentive governance (malus/clawback/deferral/gatekeeper), scheme design (which measures, LTI/commission types), eligibility-policy, sign-on (not performance-contingent), or overtime/shift premiums. Empty/absent → P4P off everywhere (degrade). If this set were every Incentives metric, output = the old coarse behaviour byte-for-byte.",
  "variable_pay_metrics": ["323ffcf1-749b-43f3-bf34-1de6b8b1ca67", "REW_INC_111", "REW_INC_104", "REW_INC_LTI_MAX_01", "REW_INC_LTI_VALUE_TYP_01", "REW_INC_131", "REW_INC_135"],
  "max_per_lens": 2,
